videos.headline: NC State RB stiff arms defender on way to TD
videos.description: Reggie Gallaspy II breaks one tackle then stiff arms another defender on his way in to a 34-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Tar Heels tie game with TD, 2-point conversion
videos.description: North Carolina RB Javonte Williams powers through for a 8-yard touchdown, then Cade Fortin converts on the pass to tie the game 21-21.
